title: HOUR 3- Nick Foles and Robert Horry Oct 09, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Nick Foles and Robert Horry Oct 09, 2020
description:
Nick Foles tells Dan that he is happy to get the win over Tampa Bay. Nick says it was like a fist fight although it was not pretty. Robert Horry tells Dan about the first time Michael Jordan spoke to him in a game. Horry tells Dan that he was the one who taught Kobe how to play spades.
